T02TD1693E:49b-3: 'phags ma sgrol ma la bstod pa /
T02TD1693E:49b-4: bcom ldan 'das 'jam pa'i dbyangs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1693E:49b-5: sgrol mdzad 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas pa //
T02TD1693E:49b-6: stod pa las sgrol thugs rje'i spyan yangs ma //
T02TD1693E:49b-7: bde gshegs yum gyur lha mo sgrol ma la //
T02TD1693E:49b-8: lus ngag yid gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1693E:49b-9: khyod kyis mdzad pa'i phrin las rgya che ba //
T02TD1693E:49b-10: ma lus brjod par sus kyang mi spobs te //
T02TD1693E:50a-0: che long rags pas rnam brgyad @50a * //
T02TD1693E:50a-2: ngo mtshar legs spyad gtam snyan 'di skad thos //
T02TD1693E:50a-3: shin tu rmad byung yon tan rgya mtsho'i gter //
T02TD1693E:50a-4: dge tshogs nor bu dam pa rin chen gling //
T02TD1693E:50a-5: sna tshogs padmo'i tshal ni dri bsung can //
T02TD1693E:50a-6: phreng mdzes tshig gi me tog mchod par bzhes //
T02TD1693E:50a-7: skal ldan rigs can lam mtshon med pa zhig / rang yul ma slebs ri dgas rgyal pos bdas //
T02TD1693E:50a-8: khom ldan skyes bus gsum la skyabs 'gro byas //
T02TD1693E:50a-9: sgrol mas rjes bzung seng ges gus phyag 'tshal //
T02TD1693E:50a-10: don gnyer 'gron la gdong dmar gangs ri'i mdog / rdul 'dzag rab khros khro gnyer mche ba gtsigs //
T02TD1693E:50a-11: byin rlabs mthar thug gzungs sngags bstod pa'i mthus //
T02TD1693E:50a-12: de ma thag tu glang chen 'jigs las skyabs //
T02TD1693E:50a-13: shing skam khri la tshe tshad brgya bzhag ste //
T02TD1693E:50a-14: log lta'i rgyal pos drang srong me lha mchod //
T02TD1693E:50a-15: thams cad mkhyen pas me tog phreng 'dzin mdzad //
T02TD1693E:50a-16: dngos su zhal bstan bdud rtsi'i char rgyun phab //
T02TD1693E:50a-17: tshong dpon nor ldan shul rings lam du zhugs //
T02TD1693E:50a-18: 'jigs pa'i thang la mi rgod chom rkun byung //
T02TD1693E:50a-19: yi dam lha mos 'jigs med bde sar bskyal //
T02TD1693E:50a-20: drin lan ma brjed rten la mchod pa phul //
T02TD1693E:50a-21: gzugs mdzes bu mos pha rol nags su phyin //
T02TD1693E:50a-22: dug sbrul gdug pa'i kha rlangs sprin ltar 'thibs //
T02TD1693E:50a-23: 'bras ldan ljon pa'i shing gi bsil grib la //
T02TD1693E:50a-24: spyi bor phyag bzhag mi bzad nad las thar //
T02TD1693E:50a-25: sbyin pa'i 'bras med dbul phongs rkun po'i mis //
T02TD1693E:50a-26: dkor mdzod blangs pas btson khang ra bar bcug / dad ldan slob mas thugs dam rgyud bskul bas //
T02TD1693E:50a-27: thugs rje'i phyag gis lcags sgrog mdud pa dkrol //
T02TD1693E:50a-28: tsandra go mi dge bsnyen 'phags pa mchog / rgyal po'i chad pas gang+g'a'i chu la bskur //
T02TD1693E:50a-29: gus ldan zhe sa bcas pa'i sdeb sbyor gyis //
T02TD1693E:50a-30: 'dzum zhal dge mas sing ga'i gling la bzhag / rgyal brgyud lam 'khrul dur khrod gnas su 'khyams //
T02TD1693E:50a-31: log 'dren 'byung po'i gdon gyis zin gyur tshe //
T02TD1693E:50a-32: rig pa'i rgyal po rig sngags bcu bzlas pas //
T02TD1693E:50a-33: bar chad bdud kyi tshogs las rgyal bar gyur //
T02TD1693E:50b-0: seng ge glang chen @50b me dang chom rkun dang //
T02TD1693E:50b-1: dug sbrul btson khang chu dang 'byung po'i gdon //
T02TD1693E:50b-2: 'dus byas rgya mtsho las 'bras 'jug ngogs can //
T02TD1693E:50b-3: byang sems klu dbang bden gnyis gtsug gi nor //
T02TD1693E:50b-4: pha rol phyin drug rin chen rgyan gyis spras //
T02TD1693E:50b-5: lnga bcu lhun grub phrin las gzi brjid can //
T02TD1693E:50b-6: 'jigs brgyad sgrol mas gzhan yang sems can gyi //
T02TD1693E:50b-7: phyi rol grub mtha' ngan pa log lta'i ri //
T02TD1693E:50b-8: lung rigs rdo rje'i mtshon gyis bcom nas kyang //
T02TD1693E:50b-9: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsum dkon mchog gsum //
T02TD1693E:50b-10: yang dag mtha' bral lta ba ma rtogs na //
T02TD1693E:50b-11: tshig gi bsnyems pas don la mi rtogs te //
T02TD1693E:50b-12: sems can gnas lugs nam mkha'i chos nyid la //
T02TD1693E:50b-13: ma rig 'khrul pa'i dra ba bsal du gsol //
T02TD1693E:50b-14: bsod nams chung bas dge ba'i sems med cing //
T02TD1693E:50b-15: mi dge'i mun bsgribs yang dag lam ma rnyed //
T02TD1693E:50b-16: bdag 'dzin bdud kyi srid mtsho 'dir 'khyams rnams //
T02TD1693E:50b-17: bshes gnyen thabs mkhas gru gzings ded dpon gyis //
T02TD1693E:50b-18: chu bzhi'i pha rol yid 'ong po ta la //
T02TD1693E:50b-19: bde mchog gnas chen lha yi pho brang du //
T02TD1693E:50b-20: 'gro kun yan lag bdun ldan chos spyod cing //
T02TD1693E:50b-21: nyer mkho'i yo byad bka' babs brgyad gnang nas //
T02TD1693E:50b-22: phrin las lha mos zhal bzhes ma bsnyel bar //
T02TD1693E:50b-23: bshes gnyen ngan pa'i bdud dang mjal ba rnams //
T02TD1693E:50b-24: dal 'byor chud zos mi tshe stong 'dzad cing //
T02TD1693E:50b-25: zas nor don med gnas su brlag gyur pa //
T02TD1693E:50b-26: lus sems sdug bsngal chu yi rba rlabs kyis //
T02TD1693E:50b-27: nyon mongs 'khrul ba'i sems can ma lus dang //
T02TD1693E:50b-28: bka' 'bangs tha ma bdag cag thams cad la //
T02TD1693E:50b-29: rnam dag thos bsam sgom gsum bstan du gsol //
T02TD1693E:50b-30: rnam dag thos bsam sgom gsum bstan nas kyang //
T02TD1693E:50b-31: phan bde'i dge ba byang chub mchog tu bsngo //
T02TD1693E:50b-32: khyod kyi phrin las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor de //
T02TD1693E:50b-33: chags sdang gti mug sprin gyi grib ma yis //
T02TD1693E:50b-34: sgrib par ma gyur dpal ldan 'phags pa'i sku //
T02TD1693E:50b-35: dge tshogs sprin chen lhun po'i rtser bzhugs la //
T02TD1693E:50b-36: sa 'dzin spol rta bdun rgyal po ltar //
T02TD1693E:50b-37: lham me lhang nger gsal ba'i bkra shis shog / gtsang bdag bde dang rtag pa nyid thob pa //
T02TD1693E:51a-2: brnyes gyur lhun gyis grub cing 'dus ma byas //
T02TD1693E:51a-3: bsam zhing brjod pa'i yul las 'das gyur kyang //
T02TD1693E:51a-4: chu nang zla ba nam mkha'i 'ja' bzhin du //
T02TD1693E:51a-5: sprul skus 'gro don mdzad par smon lam 'debs //
T02TD1693E:51a-6: klu sgrub padmo'i ge sar las //
T02TD1693E:51a-7: nyi ma sbas pa bung ba yis //
T02TD1693E:51a-8: legs blangs bdud rtsi'i dga' ston gyis //
T02TD1693E:51a-9: bu slob sbrang bu'i lus rgyas shog / kha che'i slob dpon nyi ma sbas pas rje btsun sgrol ma la bstod pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1693E:51a-11: // / rgya gar gyi pandi ta s'a dhu k'i rti dang /
T02TD1693E:51a-12: bod kyi lo ts'a ba ldan ma tshul khrims seng ges bsgyur ba las phyis dpal sa skya'i gtsug lag khang du dag par byas so//
